modShortDescription: 0W power streetlights and wire relays to allow an area on a dedicated server to be lit from a single battery bank without needing any maintenance.
modDescription:
0W power [streetlights](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-lights/) and wire relays to allow an area on a dedicated server to be lit from a single [battery](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-electricity/) bank without needing any maintenance.

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/26324-sams-stuff-all-a20-server-side-modlets/).
